          "username": "Ashley Selett",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "106498357627367774202",
          "user_review_count": 9,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnOMsr-z0jiMOK_GC2CVeTUiB0yeIKLfwc1IMBYg-ScTzA2FGp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "First, I completely messed up my appointment day, and they were unbelievably gracious and accommodating. They still took me and made me feel totally welcome. From the moment you walk in, the front desk and every single person there is genuinely happy, warm, and incredibly helpful. It\u2019s rare to feel that kind of positive energy in a medical office.\n\nMy hygienist, Myra, was so sweet and so thorough. She did my cleaning, X-rays, and scans with such care and professionalism. She made everything feel easy and comfortable.\n\nAnd Dr. Bertman, I cannot say enough. I have seen so many dentists, periodontists, and oral surgeons over the years (I\u2019m a complicated case), and he truly stands out. He is thoughtful, thorough, highly informed, and most importantly, trustworthy. He is not interested in pushing treatments or selling procedures. He listens carefully, evaluates comprehensively, and clearly only wants what\u2019s actually best for his patients.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wR1JrWmFObmgzTVVscFIxVTJNbmhUUVZvM04wRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x742671c0d1a7adab!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnpGRkZaNnh3MUlpR1U2MnhTQVo3N0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
