          "description": "If anyone has any interest in getting the absolute BEST teeth cleaning ever, book yourself an appointment with Icela.  Not only is she incredibly thorough and detail oriented, she is also proactive in identifying solutions and suggestions from a preventative perspective, so as to avoid potential problems later.  She stays abreast of all the latest dental developments and is an absolute pleasure to be around.\nI guarantee that if you have the opportunity to visit her once, you will never want to go any place else.\nThank you Icela, for all that you do!",
