          "description": "Over the course of two days, Dr. Isabelle DeMatteis (oral surgeon)  and Dr. Kim (endodontist),  gave me a root canal and also extracted a molar. I have been seeing Dr. Todd Bertman and his wonderful staff for many years but this was my first experience with Dr. Kim and Dr. DeMatteis and both were outstanding.  I actually didn't feel Dr. Kim's numbing injections at all and he worked quickly, with great precision.  Dr.DeMatteis, who performed my molar extraction, was exceptionally kind and gave me just enough info during the procedure to let me know all was going as it should. The techs who worked with each dentist were stellar. I hate going to the dentist but I love Advanced Dental Arts. They are a ten star dental practice!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKakxUWklRbmxtZEhWR1dsWk9hVW93VDFReFJFRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x742671c0d1a7adab!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlJjLTZIQnlmdHVGWlZOaUowT1QxREE%7C%7C?hl=en",
